01:29:55.958 --> 01:29:59.998
I mean, I thought he would diagnose you
with schizophrenia or something.

01:30:00.625 --> 01:30:03.415
Are you sure you don't want
to take a look? She's tremendous.

01:30:03.500 --> 01:30:05.140
You're the one who'll end up
schizophrenic

01:30:05.292 --> 01:30:07.372
if you keep talking to people
while looking at photos

01:30:07.417 --> 01:30:08.207
of hot women.

01:30:08.375 --> 01:30:10.785
I don't want to forget
there's a world out there.

01:30:10.958 --> 01:30:13.038
Because there's something worse
than dark energy.

01:30:13.125 --> 01:30:16.285
Shit, Pablo. I can't mix physics
with my feelings anymore.

01:30:16.417 --> 01:30:19.417
Dark matter is much worse.

01:30:19.625 --> 01:30:20.625
No!

01:30:25.958 --> 01:30:27.288
You two are having a baby?

01:30:27.458 --> 01:30:29.918
Eva was right when she said
down deep I'm a great dad.

01:30:30.000 --> 01:30:32.480
Congratulations, man! <i>We don't know</i>
<i>what dark matter is either.</i>

01:30:36.708 --> 01:30:40.208
<i>What we do know is that the universe
behaves like there was more gravity</i>

01:30:40.375 --> 01:30:43.415
<i>than corresponds to the bodies
we can see.</i>

01:30:43.750 --> 01:30:46.500
<i>That means we attract
and cling to each other</i>

01:30:46.708 --> 01:30:49.498
<i>more than we should
according to how attractive we are.</i>

01:30:49.708 --> 01:30:51.168
Here's your lunch.

01:30:57.250 --> 01:30:59.830
Good lord, what am I doing?

01:31:00.125 --> 01:31:03.125
Things were going so well,
why did I have to fall in love?

01:31:03.292 --> 01:31:05.632
You say that dark energy
could be fear.

01:31:05.833 --> 01:31:09.503
Well, I say that dark matter
is necessity.

01:31:09.917 --> 01:31:11.827
And necessity sucks.

01:31:12.250 --> 01:31:15.330
What I liked was entropy,
disorder.

01:31:16.000 --> 01:31:18.250
That was my territory.
And I'll tell you something else:

01:31:18.417 --> 01:31:21.957
with less entropy, there's less
freedom, because the particles

01:31:22.083 --> 01:31:24.173
are tied down!

01:31:24.458 --> 01:31:25.918
Isn't that right?

01:31:26.167 --> 01:31:27.167
Am I right or not?

01:31:27.208 --> 01:31:29.288
I don't know, I'm not listening.

01:31:30.292 --> 01:31:32.292
For God's sake!

01:31:33.458 --> 01:31:36.748
I need entropy back in my life!

01:31:51.042 --> 01:31:55.382
<i>There's still one law missing to
complete our voyage through science:</i>

01:31:55.542 --> 01:31:58.212
<i>the third principle
of thermodynamics.</i>

01:32:10.875 --> 01:32:13.075
- We'll be at the bar.
- Okay.

01:32:49.375 --> 01:32:50.955
<i>That's right,</i>

01:32:51.083 --> 01:32:53.383
<i>we'll never be able
to completely forget.</i>

01:32:53.542 --> 01:32:55.882
<i>We'll never reach that temperature
that stops</i>

01:32:56.000 --> 01:32:58.080
<i>our atoms from vibrating
when we see her.</i>

01:32:58.542 --> 01:33:00.212
Congratulations, Elena.

01:33:03.167 --> 01:33:04.707
Thanks for coming.

01:33:04.875 --> 01:33:06.705
It was very important to me.

01:33:07.917 --> 01:33:09.417
Congratulations.

01:33:09.583 --> 01:33:11.173
I hope you two are very happy.

01:33:11.833 --> 01:33:13.213
It's Manel, my ex.

01:33:13.375 --> 01:33:14.955
Manel, thanks for coming.

01:33:15.125 --> 01:33:16.995
I hope you enjoy the party.

01:33:17.250 --> 01:33:19.750
- Elena, look who's here!
- Victor, great to see you!

01:33:19.875 --> 01:33:20.955
Congratulations, beautiful.

01:33:30.042 --> 01:33:31.832
Hi.

01:33:32.250 --> 01:33:33.250
Raquel?

01:33:34.208 --> 01:33:35.828
What are you doing here?

01:33:35.958 --> 01:33:37.708
Small world, huh?

01:33:38.250 --> 01:33:39.880
I'm a friend of Lorenzo's.

01:33:40.583 --> 01:33:44.583
Well, actually we had our own
quantum entanglement.

01:33:48.542 --> 01:33:49.832
He's a good guy.

01:33:50.125 --> 01:33:52.125
And he's very hot.

01:33:53.750 --> 01:33:55.580
But I liked you more.

01:33:57.583 --> 01:33:58.793
<i>There you have it.</i>

01:33:59.125 --> 01:34:02.785
<i>Once thermodynamics comes
into your life, it never leaves.</i>

01:34:02.958 --> 01:34:04.788
Hey, it's Raquel!

01:34:04.958 --> 01:34:06.578
- Pablito!
- How are you?

01:34:06.792 --> 01:34:09.462
The best girlfriend
this bum ever had!

01:34:10.125 --> 01:34:12.575
This is Eva, the best girlfriend
<i>this</i> bum ever had.

01:34:12.792 --> 01:34:14.332
- Nice to meet you.
- Likewise.

01:34:23.250 --> 01:34:27.330
<i>Although, thanks to my therapy,
I was able to reflect</i>

01:34:27.583 --> 01:34:31.293
<i>and I've discovered the law
that truly rules over all of our actions.</i>

01:34:32.042 --> 01:34:35.422
<i>It's no doubt the most amazing law
of all time.</i>

01:34:35.917 --> 01:34:38.747
<i>But we'll leave it for next time.</i>
